  ('judicial-ae9cc487-moex-00024', 'judicial-ae9cc487', 'judicial-ae9cc487-moex-113-de0a21a2', 'sub-judicial-ae9cc487-01', NULL, 'essay', '甲、乙為朋友，乙在賣場銷售手錶，某日甲在乙工作時探望乙，且在兩人
