  ('judicial-ae9cc487-moex-00025', 'judicial-ae9cc487', 'judicial-ae9cc487-moex-113-de0a21a2', 'sub-judicial-ae9cc487-01', NULL, 'essay', '甲、乙為戀人，某日甲發現乙將兩人合意拍攝的性私密影片給甲的好友
