的熟悉程度（FamiliaritywithTechnology）、專案規模（ProjectSize）。（15分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:25:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "30f55c6306f0", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113120", "c": "109", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "系統分析", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試司法人員考試、法務部調查局調查人員考試、海岸巡防人員考試、未具擬任職務任用資格取得法官遴選資格考試", "original_question_number": "一", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "judicial", "civil_category": "檢察事務官-電子資訊組"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('judicial-ae9cc487-moex-00031', 'judicial-ae9cc487', 'judicial-ae9cc487-moex-113-579e3022', 'sub-judicial-ae9cc487-03', NULL, 'essay', '公部門為了增加政府運作的透明度，使公眾能夠了解政府的決策過程和
